Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(77.6,246)\c&HE4E9EA&\fad(500,1000)}前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个人名叫德纳迪埃  他救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A man called Thenardier saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你今后遇见他  尽你所能款待他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you meet him, do the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在需要的只是点燃炸药桶的火花\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All we need now is a spark to set off the powder keg,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后全巴黎都会陷入火海\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and all Paris could go up in flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要让城市失控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must make this city ungovernable!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誓死守卫我们的街垒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And defend this barricade to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你们找到那个人  逮捕他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want that man found, arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他移送法办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and brought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谁  -冉·阿让\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who? - Jean Valjean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去一个秘密住所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're moving to a secret address.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那别人怎么找我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how would anyone know how to find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想有人来找你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there someone you wish to be found by?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.19,0:00:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲爱的马吕斯  今晚请过来  或者捎个信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My beloved Marius, please come or send word tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有封信要给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a letter for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能让你出去  巴黎到处都在打仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't let you go! There's fighting all over Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的心已经飞走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In her heart, she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七号的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got a letter for number seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的  现在我和朋友们在街垒上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My darling, I am now on the barricades with my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我死了  我爱你至死不渝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I die, I die loving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\t(0,1200,\blur0)\fad(0,0)\fs35\t(200,9000,\fs45)\a10\c&H1603C0&\pos(195,81.9)}悲惨世界\N\N\N\N{\fs24}第一季  第六集  [剧终]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都结束了  同志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all over, comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成百名士兵正准备进攻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hundreds of soldiers are getting ready to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多数街垒都被摧毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And most of the barricades have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再好不过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都出去  你们都得听听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody outside, now. You need to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯  古费拉克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marius. Courfeyrac.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市民们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的时刻到来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This...is the endgame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下来继续战斗就等于选择死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every man and woman who stays here and fights today will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史会铭记我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}History will remember us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天人民会胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and one day the people will prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在  全巴黎的军队都出动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, for now, the whole Paris army is out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小时之内我们就会交锋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and within an hour they will be upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有希望了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have nothing to expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一点希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing to hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把街垒筑得更高些  战斗到最后一人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's raise the barrier higher, and fight till the last man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们  想想吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Friends, consider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有妻子丈夫  儿子女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some of you have wives, husbands, sons, daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英勇牺牲对他们无益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A heroic death will do nothing for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被杀  他们就会挨饿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You get yourself killed, they starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至更惨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们活下来才更勇敢  为了你们的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For you, it is a braver thing to live, for your family's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安灼拉说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enjolras is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们活下去  改日再战  这没什么可丢脸的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no shame on you living to fight another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有已婚的人  有家要养的人  站出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every married man and woman, every breadwinner, come forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们握手告别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}shake our hands, and leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我命令你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I command you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恳求你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I entreat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好活下去  同志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Live well, comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要创造一个更美好的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be building a better world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个我们看不到的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A world we won't be seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定你要留在这吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you quite sure you want to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bonjour, mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到我爸爸了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you seen Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  回来  小姐  回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mademoiselle, come back! Mademoiselle, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prepare yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mademoiselle! Mademoiselle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-回去  回去  -马吕斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get back! Get back! - Marius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别上街  -马吕斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get back off the street! - Marius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-快看  -就位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Look! - Positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prepare yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brace yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cannon fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上  上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Allez! Allez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们撤退了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're falling back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公民  共和国感谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Citizen, the Republic thanks you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认识你  也不知道你为什么来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know who you are, or why you are here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很高兴你来加入我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm glad to have you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个严峻的历史时刻...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a grim moment in our history...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,.. 但也是光辉的一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..but a glorious one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的牺牲将有助于建设一个更好的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our sacrifice is going to help build a better world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个街垒不仅仅是用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This barricade is made of more than
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石块和床架建成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just cobblestones and bedsteads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是由同胞们的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is made of hopes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of ideals,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爱建成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of love of our fellow men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为这世上所有不幸的人而战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We fight for the wretched of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便我们会死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if we go to our deaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是慷慨赴义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we go to our deaths with joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共和国万岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long live the Republic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,革命万岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vive la revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯  马吕斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marius! Marius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们争取了一些时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've bought ourselves some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是我们快没有子弹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The trouble is, we're running out of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加夫罗什  加夫罗什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gavroche! Gavroche!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加夫罗什  回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gavroche, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加夫罗什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gavroche!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会让自己送命的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加夫罗什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gavroche!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运气不好  再来呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bad luck, try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加夫罗什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gavroche!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好枪法...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别犯傻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  马吕斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quickly, Marius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有子弹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿赌服输...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was good sport...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的小东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poor little squirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说愿赌服输\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said it was good sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安灼拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enjolras!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他弄屋里  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get him inside, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把他扶起来  -包扎一下伤口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get him up. - Dress his wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯  马吕斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marius. Marius!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睁开眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们最后的阵地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is our last refuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们攻占了街垒以后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When they take the barricade,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着人的可以在这继续战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}those left alive can fight on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个奸细警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The police spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一个活着的人可以朝他头上开一枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The last man alive can put a bullet in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能来执行这光荣的使命吗  行行好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I claim that honour? As a favour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他归你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快  同志们  走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, comrades. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本该如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来报仇吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take your revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用刀子才更像你的风格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A blade would be more your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自由了  快走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're free. Now go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能活下来  虽说希望不大...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I come through this alive, which isn't very likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,.. 你可以来武人街抓我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..you can find me at Rue de l'Homme-Arme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Number seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不会拒捕的  -你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I shan't resist arrest. - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没理由要你的命  趁我改主意之前赶紧走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've no reason to take your life. Now go, before I change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想把握住杀我的机会吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you're not going to take your opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想死吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you wish to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这总比放了我要说得通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would make a hell of a lot more sense than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那你只能自己去寻死了  现在赶紧走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, you'll have to arrange it yourself. Now go. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来  回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古费拉克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Courfeyrac!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会载入史册  这会载入史册\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is history. This is history.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找你自己的酒鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find your own boozer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计 那真疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bugger, that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是带头的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-朝他站的地方开枪  -等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shoot him where he stands. - Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共和国万岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long live the Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排好队  伙计们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Line up, lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有权选择蒙上眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're entitled to be blindfolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你们想要眼罩吗  -去你妈的眼罩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you want the blindfold? - I piss on your blindfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24601\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}24601
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人是罪犯  骗子和小偷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This man is a criminal, a liar and a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人间的渣滓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The scum of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个肮脏的小偷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a dirty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是他的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到这个恶魔了吗  恶魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see this monster? Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是他的错  罪犯  骗子  小偷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all his fault. ..Criminal, liar and a thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肮脏的小偷  恶魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dirty thief! Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人间的渣滓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scum of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肮脏的小偷  人间的渣滓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dirty thief! Scum of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.97,0:23:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨你  恶魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate you! Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-站住  -退下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hold it there! - Get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.78,0:24:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来了  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're back, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.50,0:24:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.86,0:24:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见  里韦特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you see, Rivette.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.18,0:24:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有报告称你被叛军抓住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..There was a report that you'd been captured by the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.15,0:24:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而我在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.32,0:25:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到他了吗  你追的那个人  冉阿让\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you see him? The one you're after, that man Valjean?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.86,0:25:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我见到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.38,0:25:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了  他被抓起来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened? Is he in custody?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.47,0:25:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.18,0:25:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He got away?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.25,0:25:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他放我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He allowed me to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.96,0:25:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你也有心软的时候  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must have a soft spot for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.39,0:25:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在嘲笑我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you mocking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.56,0:25:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.22,0:25:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些叛军都被杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know they were all killed, the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.05,0:25:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他的尸体找到了吗  -不知道  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Was his body found with the others? - Don't know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.03,0:25:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他依然在逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then he's still at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.59,0:25:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有另一个人  德纳迪埃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the other fella, Thenardier,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.18,0:26:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人看到他在河边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's been sighted down by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.46,0:26:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于暴乱  这些人渣都冒出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These riots seem to have brought all the scum to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.14,0:26:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚正打算去那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just on my way down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.10,0:26:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意一起来吗  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you wish to come, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.88,0:26:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最精锐的人手已经准备好了  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got some of our best men standing by, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.42,0:26:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think there's a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.98,0:26:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-能把他们一锅端  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- we might net the whole gang of them. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.40,0:26:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好  里韦特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done, Rivette.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.65,0:26:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请允许我  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just permit me, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.33,0:26:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手拿开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take your hands off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.33,0:26:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.86,0:26:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.79,0:27:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.43,0:27:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.90,0:27:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.26,0:27:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住  撑住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay alive. Stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.24,0:27:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay... Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.04,0:27:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯·彭眉胥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marius Pontmercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.22,0:27:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.44,0:28:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我死了  把我的遗体带给我的祖父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I die, take my body to my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.72,0:28:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉诺曼先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Gillenormand,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.47,0:28:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受难修女街六号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}number six, Rue des Filles-du-Calvaire...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.08,0:31:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you...you're really in the shit, aren't you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.73,0:31:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.04,0:31:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅  天呐  这味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me. Ooh! The smell of you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.93,0:31:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不属于这里吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're really not at home here, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.24,0:31:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不了解这里的路  你不属于这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know your way around, it's not your milieu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.50,0:31:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.57,0:31:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想知道你现在要怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm just wondering about what you're going to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.86,0:31:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要如何走出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you're going to get out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.35,0:31:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.38,0:31:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被困住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.69,0:31:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真尴尬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.69,0:31:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以前也算不上朋友  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've not been friends in the past, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.62,0:31:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在可以帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I could help you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.65,0:31:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把你在那个人口袋里找到的分我一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You give me half of what you've found in that man's pockets,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.44,0:31:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就帮你打开门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I'll open up the gate for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.31,0:31:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What makes you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.13,0:31:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他口袋里有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..He had anything in his pockets?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.81,0:31:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是他有值得拥有的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you wouldn't have killed him
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.93,0:31:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不会杀了他  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}unless he had something worth having, now, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.20,0:31:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五五分  怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you say, 50/50?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.31,0:31:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.37,0:32:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要打开这扇门吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you going to get this gate open?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.59,0:32:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, no need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.42,0:32:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是我的地盘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is my territory down here, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.70,0:32:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在先看看你有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let's see what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.43,0:32:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊  我们来交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Let's trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.97,0:32:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这  好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There. Ye-e-e-es!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.98,0:32:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这些吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.53,0:32:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为这么点东西割断一个人的喉咙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not much for slitting a man's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.23,0:32:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在这了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.35,0:32:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十法郎  你确定吗  不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten francs? Are you sure? With your permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.51,0:32:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手伸出来  伸出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arms out. Arms out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.04,0:32:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世道也抢不到多少了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hardly worth it these days, is it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.35,0:32:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成王败寇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The robbery game.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都没什么钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No-one's got nothing no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.03,0:32:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  先生  我带你出去  带上你的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, mister, I'll let you out. Take your friend with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.70,0:32:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你想丢下他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find a rope,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.45,0:32:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就找根绳子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tie it around a big stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.11,0:32:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他绑在一块大石头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...when you dump him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.37,0:32:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望他再冒出来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't want him bobbing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.45,0:33:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.37,0:33:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走啊  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on. Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.03,0:33:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.76,0:33:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.67,0:33:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你毁了我的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ruined my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.80,0:33:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾受人尊敬  也曾富有过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was a respected man. I had money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.85,0:33:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我像老鼠一样生活在黑暗中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I live like a rat in the shitty darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.42,0:34:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.37,0:35:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是冉·阿让  沙威探长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Jean Valjean. Inspector Javert,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.86,0:35:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您现在就可以逮捕我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can take me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.87,0:35:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但请帮我个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but grant me one favour.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.01,0:35:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我把这个人带回家见他的祖父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me take this man home to his grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.80,0:35:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.57,0:35:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫马吕斯·彭眉胥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His name's Marius Pontmercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.88,0:35:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他受伤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.85,0:35:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他看起来死了  -不  还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He looks dead. - No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.53,0:35:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.07,0:35:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您能帮我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.74,0:35:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.44,0:36:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉诺曼先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Gillenormand!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.42,0:36:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门  警察  开门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open up. Police! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.79,0:36:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你家主人我们带回来了他孙子的尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell your master we've brought his grandson's body home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.18,0:37:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说他孙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His grandson, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.13,0:37:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天  是马吕斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God, it's Monsieur Marius.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.02,0:37:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻点  小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gently! Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.14,0:37:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是马吕斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Monsieur Marius!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.19,0:37:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻点  轻点  小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gently, gently. Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.17,0:37:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Merci, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.03,0:37:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯先生  他们对你做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Marius, what have they done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.68,0:37:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要告诉我  他死了  他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ahhhh, no need to tell me... He's dead! He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.00,0:37:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在街垒上被杀  只是为了忤逆我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's got himself killed on the barricades, just to defy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.34,0:37:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很清楚我在等他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knew very well I was waiting for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.79,0:37:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你非得这么做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You...you had to do it, didn't you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.23,0:37:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤一个老人的心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you had to break an old man's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.45,0:38:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  先生  我能感觉到脉搏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait! Monsieur! I can feel a pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.46,0:38:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝保佑他会活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pray God he'll live!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.28,0:38:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中士  中士  快  把他带上楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Serge! Serge! Quickly, get him upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.11,0:38:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来  过来  快  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on! Come on! Quickly! Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.22,0:38:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.45,0:38:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再帮我一个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One more favour.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.57,0:38:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我回趟家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.20,0:38:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要几分钟就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just for a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.81,0:38:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我便听凭你处置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you can do with me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.34,0:38:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准许\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.21,0:39:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.56,0:39:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is he a...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.88,0:39:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很特别的朋友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}particular friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.02,0:39:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你珍视的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you say he's...dear to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.93,0:39:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰恰相反\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quite the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.95,0:39:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他活着  他打算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he lives, he intends to...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.37,0:39:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢走我全部的幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}rob me of...all my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.57,0:39:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你却...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.47,0:39:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.22,0:39:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.43,0:40:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.86,0:40:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里等你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll wait for you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.52,0:40:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.77,0:40:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.79,0:41:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.94,0:41:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你能找到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you can find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.65,0:42:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Javert?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.83,0:42:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Javert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.41,0:42:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Javert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.70,0:42:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}沙威
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.43,0:43:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.03,0:43:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为警务系统的更高效运转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been making some recommendations
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.63,0:43:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提了一些建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the more efficient running of the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.06,0:43:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我委托你一个任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I entrust you with the task of bringing them
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.79,0:43:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这些建议呈给长官们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the attention of the commissioners.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.71,0:43:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.89,0:43:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All well?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.53,0:43:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.10,0:43:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里韦特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rivette...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.81,0:43:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All is not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.95,0:43:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囚犯阿让\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prisoner Valjean.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.76,0:43:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不再是囚犯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's no longer a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.07,0:43:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.95,0:43:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放他自由了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I let him go free.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.55,0:43:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能问问原因吗  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I ask why, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.74,0:43:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.45,0:44:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种仁慈之举吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As an act of clemency?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.30,0:44:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是疯狂之举\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An act of madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.47,0:44:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.90,0:44:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That man!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.81,0:44:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我此生深信不疑的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything I've ever believed to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.64,0:44:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有我毕生遵循的原则...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything I lived my life by...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.18,0:44:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.36,0:44:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.24,0:45:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不重要了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.00,0:45:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我将辞去我的职务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shall, of course, be resigning my commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.76,0:45:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  长官  一个错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really, sir, one mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.61,0:45:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算真的是错误  为一个错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it is indeed a mistake, one mistake against...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.01,0:45:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-而辞职...  -经历了这种事  我怎么继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- a long career... - How can I continue? After this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.59,0:45:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让我自己和警局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have brought myself and the police service
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.98,0:45:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒙受耻辱和污名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}into disgrace and disrepute.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.20,0:45:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要新鲜空气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.33,0:45:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出去走走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.83,0:45:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得把这些建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember to bring those notes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.25,0:45:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呈给警务总监\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the attention of the Prefect of Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.45,0:45:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  里韦特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodnight, Rivette.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.32,0:46:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总监先生  我请求您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I beg, Monsieur Le Prefet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.04,0:46:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑以下几点对改善警务工作的建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to consider these proposals for improvements to the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.88,0:46:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一  我们应当终止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First, that we end the practice of prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.63,0:46:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在从审问归来的囚犯们等待被转移回监狱时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}returning from interrogations being made to remove their shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.25,0:46:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强迫他们脱掉鞋子的规程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while they await transport back to the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.11,0:46:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多人在回到牢房时都在咳嗽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Many are coughing when they return to their cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.52,0:46:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这将加大医疗开支\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This leads to hospital expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.13,0:46:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二  在纺织间掉下一根线的囚犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Second, a prisoner who drops a thread in the weaving room
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.49,0:46:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将被罚十苏  这是滥用...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}loses 10 sous. This is an abuse of...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.53,0:46:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三  对于特殊规定...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Third, the special regulation of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.76,0:46:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四  通常情况下监视...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fourth, surveillance is generally...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.39,0:46:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五  警察们...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fifth, gendarmes...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.85,0:46:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,返回的囚犯们...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prisoners coming back from the...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.02,0:49:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,革命万岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vive la revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.50,0:49:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ssh, Marius...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.49,0:49:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.79,0:49:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲爱的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My dear boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.47,0:49:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么到这来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did I end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.07,0:49:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被警察带到这来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were carried here by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.98,0:50:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.41,0:50:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是街垒上的一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somebody else. At the barricade.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.02,0:50:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我欠他一条命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I owe him my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.59,0:50:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都死了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are they all dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.09,0:50:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安灼拉  古费拉克  格朗泰尔  所有朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enjolras, Courfeyrac, Grantaire - all my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.01,0:50:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It...would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.08,0:50:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都白白牺牲了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it all for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.80,0:50:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把你带回了我身边  我最亲爱的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It brought you back to me, my dearest boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.85,0:51:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想结婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.41,0:51:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.87,0:51:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听见没  他现在想结婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you hear that? He wants to be married now!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.70,0:51:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都安排好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.51,0:51:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.55,0:51:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这个意思  你应该跟你的心上人在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I say. You shall have your little sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.06,0:51:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我调查了一下  发现她个百年难见的好姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done some investigating, and I find she's a jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.56,0:51:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她喜欢你  所以不用多说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she adores you. So, no more to be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.85,0:51:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珂赛特同意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cosette agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.91,0:51:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱情同意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.05,0:51:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我由衷地感到高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't...be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.53,0:51:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心爱的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My beloved child.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.71,0:51:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.99,0:52:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听见没  "父亲"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you hear that? "Father"!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.86,0:52:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是爱我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he loves me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.91,0:52:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他得到心爱的姑娘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now he's getting the girl he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.33,0:52:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.46,0:52:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请进  先生  -马吕斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ah, come in, monsieur. - Marius!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.34,0:52:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.36,0:52:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-珂赛特  -请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cosette... - Please, please, take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.04,0:52:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.67,0:52:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.90,0:52:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.24,0:52:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个不认识的人把我带回了你身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone, I don't know who, brought me back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.46,0:52:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真走运  孩子  要是我年轻个15岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're very lucky, my boy. If I were 15 years younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.02,0:52:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就要拔剑决斗决定谁能娶她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'd be drawing swords to see which of us would have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.40,0:52:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.80,0:52:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  我不能也爱上她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the matter? Can't I be in love with her too?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.49,0:52:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.96,0:52:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的  小姐  他属于你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm joking, Mademoiselle. He's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.85,0:52:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有了一位称职的英俊丈夫了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a handsome husband worth his salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.91,0:53:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担心钱的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.20,0:53:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的外祖父会照顾你们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your grandpapa will take care of the pair of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.39,0:53:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我女儿有嫁妆的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, my daughter has...has a dowry.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.75,0:53:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六十五万法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}650,000 francs.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.63,0:53:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-六十五万法郎  -都在这了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 650,000 francs?! - It's all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.36,0:53:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个幸运儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you lucky devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.72,0:53:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的小宝贝还是个大富翁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your little dove turns out to be a millionairess!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.29,0:53:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不在乎钱  先生  他们只在乎彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They don't care, monsieur. The only care about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.38,0:53:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻人都这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, what it is to be young!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.25,0:53:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先告辞了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'll...take my leave, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.15,0:53:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不  我不同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no. I won't hear of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.45,0:53:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们是幸福的一家人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all one happy family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.96,0:53:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-留下来吃晚餐吧  -不了  先生  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Stay for dinner. - No, monsieur, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.24,0:53:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是请你允许我先告辞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But with your permission, I'll take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.24,0:53:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  珂赛特  你就在这吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you later, Cosette. No need for you to come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.35,0:53:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  爸爸  再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very well, Papa. I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.01,0:53:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.91,0:54:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么需要帮忙的吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can I do for you, monsieur?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.39,0:54:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕  我得坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid I... I have to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.36,0:54:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事要告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.72,0:55:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有前科\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am an ex-convict.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.65,0:55:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十年前坐过牢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}20 years in the prison hulks.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.28,0:55:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃狱了  又被抓了回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Escaped, recaptured.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.74,0:55:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又逃狱了  现在我正在被通缉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Escaped again. And presently I'm a wanted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.31,0:55:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个贼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.29,0:55:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我偷了一位主教的东西  迪涅主教\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I stole from a bishop, the Bishop of Digne.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.72,0:55:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还抢过一个小孩的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I even robbed a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.61,0:55:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是珂赛特的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You - Cosette's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.36,0:55:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不是她的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I'm not her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.47,0:55:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个孤儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.95,0:55:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我找到了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.36,0:55:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个无名之辈  法沃罗勒的农民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am no-one. I'm a peasant from Faverolles.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.90,0:55:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我犯下的第一个罪行是偷了一块面包\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My first crime was to steal a loaf of bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.67,0:55:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you see? I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.84,0:55:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个苦役犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a common criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.44,0:55:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew there was something.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.11,0:55:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得  在客栈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember, at the tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.38,0:55:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你朝那个警察开了枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shot that police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.93,0:55:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来街垒就是为了杀他  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that why you came to the barricade, to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.56,0:56:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那如果我说我来街垒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if I told you I came to the barricades
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.25,0:56:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里是抱有杀你的想法呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with half a mind to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.59,0:56:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  这就是你的处境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, you see, that's what you're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.27,0:56:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.65,0:56:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如今该怎么看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What am I to think of you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.38,0:56:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你随便怎么看我都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think of me as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.32,0:56:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想让你知道真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted you to know the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.59,0:56:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我可以平静地离开你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that I could take my leave of her, and you, in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.49,0:56:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不属于任何人的家庭  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't belong in the family of men, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.75,0:56:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是外人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.50,0:56:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的珂赛特  等她发现你走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poor Cosette! When she finds out...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.05,0:56:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别  我求求你  先生  别告诉她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I beg you, monsieur, I beg you. Spare her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.97,0:56:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能要求我不告诉她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't ask me to keep this from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.11,0:56:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.21,0:56:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有天她和我在一起的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..One day, when she was with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.89,0:56:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看见一群犯人经过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..She saw the chain gang go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.74,0:57:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她忍不住开始想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she couldn't bear to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.37,0:57:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种像我一样的坏人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..That such wicked men existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.99,0:57:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然依然存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Men like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.49,0:57:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你保守了这个秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you keep my secret, I promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.52,0:57:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证在婚礼结束之后就永远在你们的生活里消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that after the wedding I shall get out of your lives forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.91,0:57:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.58,0:57:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.89,0:57:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安  彭眉胥男爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good day, Baron Pontmercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.56,0:57:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你一生幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.66,0:58:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真漂亮啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, elle est jolie!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.91,0:58:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸爸  -怎么了亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Papa? - Yes, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.44,0:58:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.21,0:58:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然开心  为你感到开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Course I'm happy. Happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.51,0:58:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么不笑呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why aren't you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.29,0:58:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想念你  所以笑不出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just... I'm going to miss you. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.61,0:58:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样想  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be silly, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.80,0:58:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜月很快就结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The honeymoon will be over before we know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.84,0:58:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我六周后就回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I'll be back in six weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.42,0:58:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我们又可以一直见面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And...then we will see each other all of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.44,1:00:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\t(0,1200,\blur0)\fad(0,0)\fs35\t(200,9000,\fs45)\a10\c&H1603C0&\pos(195,81.9)}六周后
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.68,1:00:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  我终于到家啦  -辛苦了  伙计们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. I'm glad to be home. - Thank you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.24,1:00:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是觉得我们应该先去看爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I still think we should go and see Papa first.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.02,1:00:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定想知道我们的蜜月旅程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll be wanting to know all about our wedding journey.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.34,1:00:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-一会儿的吧  来  亲爱的  -尼科莱特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maybe later. Come on, darling. - Nicolette!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.46,1:00:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madame!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.19,1:00:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.69,1:00:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢先生  -欢迎回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Merci, monsieur. - Oh, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.05,1:00:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有个来访者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah. There's a visitor to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.16,1:00:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说事情非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very important, the gentleman said.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.92,1:00:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我让他在客厅等候  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I put him in the drawing-room. - Very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.77,1:01:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  男爵先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bonjour, Monsieur Le Baron.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.98,1:01:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.40,1:01:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我是来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur, I just thought I'd congratulate you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.48,1:01:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您新婚快乐的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on your wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.20,1:01:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  您看起来美极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, Madame, you look so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.31,1:01:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还记得我们刚在蒙费梅伊见到你的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I remember when you were a skinny little guttersnipe
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.75,1:01:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是个瘦得皮包骨的流浪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we picked up at Montfermeil.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.03,1:01:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德纳迪埃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thenardier.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.30,1:01:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  就是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.30,1:01:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯  这个人很坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marius, this man is evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.26,1:01:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候是我爸爸把我从他手里救下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father saved me from him when I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.18,1:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.52,1:01:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来给你讲讲你的爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me tell you something about your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.26,1:01:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-珂赛特  上楼去  我来处理  -你想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cosette, go upstairs, I'll deal with this. - What do you want here?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.44,1:01:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到一点消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got some information
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.45,1:01:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听完可以让你头发都竖起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for you that'll make your hair stand on end.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.21,1:02:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么消息  -我想要一点回报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What information? - I want a little something in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.75,1:02:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去新大陆那边的拉贺拉做个小生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to set up a business. In La Jolla. The New World.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.81,1:02:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有钱可赚  有奴隶可交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's money to be made there, slaves to trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.89,1:02:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你的消息是什么  -珂赛特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And your information is? - Cosette.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.63,1:02:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个老男人  你所谓的爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That old fella, your so-called father,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.96,1:02:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个飞贼兼刺客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is a thief and an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.18,1:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是你  我不会容许他在这个家里  不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't have him in the house if I was you. Not safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.25,1:02:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.22,1:02:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自己告诉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He told me so himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.26,1:02:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.48,1:02:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都杀过谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who did he kill, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.91,1:02:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他杀了那个沙威督察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He killed the police spy, Javert.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.49,1:02:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  珂赛特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Cosette.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.18,1:02:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I... It's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.94,1:02:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会相信这样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could you believe such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.75,1:02:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说得对  因为他没死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's right. Cos he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.54,1:02:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙威自杀的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Javert did himself in.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.56,1:03:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到的  从桥上跳下去死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw it with my own eyes. Threw himself off a bridge, he did.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.47,1:03:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老家伙杀了一个年轻的小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah, the one that the old fella killed was a young chap.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.23,1:03:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在他杀死他以后在下水道里见到了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I met him in the sewers just after he'd done it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.98,1:03:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本来准备把那个小伙子扔进河里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was going to dump the young chap in the river.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.88,1:03:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小伙子长什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did he look like, this young chap?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.39,1:03:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他个头差不多  我不知道  你想说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About his size. I don't know. What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.00,1:03:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你全弄错了  你这个老蠢货\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've got it all wrong, you old fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.45,1:03:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他救了你的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was saving your life!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.63,1:03:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是他把你带回家的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He must have been the man that carried you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.13,1:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.23,1:03:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他救了你的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.65,1:03:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.84,1:04:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.34,1:04:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本来是想抹黑一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came here to ruin a man...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.04,1:04:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却无心让他变得无比光辉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..And you crowned him with glory.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.42,1:04:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是个骗子  还很愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a liar, and a stupid one at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.64,1:04:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是个骗子  你是杀人犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're the thief, you're the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.83,1:04:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到你在那个肮脏的贫民窟做的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw what you did in that squalid slum.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.90,1:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以上你下半辈子都在监狱里度过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could have you chained up for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.79,1:04:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我改变主意之前  别想重见天日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now get out before I change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.65,1:04:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.10,1:04:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.99,1:04:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一千法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}1,000 francs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.36,1:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在滑铁卢战争中救了我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand you saved my father's life at Waterloo.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.48,1:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个上校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Colonel...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.08,1:05:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彭眉胥男爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..Baron Pontmercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.15,1:05:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男爵先生和夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur and Madame Pontmercy, er...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.15,1:05:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经还是善有善报的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..Once in a lifetime, virtue is rewarded, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.43,1:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My eternal gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.15,1:05:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Papa? Papa!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.78,1:05:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珂赛特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cosette?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.74,1:06:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gone away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.64,1:06:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些烛台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The candlesticks -
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.85,1:06:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.80,1:06:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉我一直瞒着你  珂赛特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I kept the truth from you, Cosette.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.26,1:06:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你父亲保证过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made a promise to your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.26,1:06:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marius...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.73,1:06:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我知道他可能在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..I think I know where he might be.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.08,1:07:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Papa?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.91,1:07:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.35,1:08:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.66,1:08:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've come?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.82,1:08:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带走了烛台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You took the candlesticks.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.88,1:08:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就觉得我们也许能来迪涅找到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought we might find you in Digne.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.75,1:08:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了我的命  却从来没有告诉过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saved my life, and never told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.27,1:08:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, monsieur...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.23,1:08:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我以后再也见不到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I'd never see her again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.82,1:08:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珂赛特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cosette.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.04,1:08:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.75,1:08:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道我不值得你的爱吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't you know, I'm not worthy of your love?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.32,1:08:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不值得任何人的爱  -别这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not worthy of anybody's love. - Don't speak like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.76,1:08:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.44,1:09:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要离开躲起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you run away and hide?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.36,1:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh... Oh, Papa! Papa...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.22,1:09:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  你的手  好冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Papa, your hands, they're so cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.69,1:09:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我快要死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's because I'm going to die soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.73,1:09:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.80,1:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.67,1:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会的  因为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You won't, because...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.66,1:09:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不会让你死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.95,1:09:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要和我们一起回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're coming home with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.64,1:09:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要绑架你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to kidnap you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.30,1:09:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的爱我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you really love me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.90,1:09:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Papa. Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.60,1:10:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you still there?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.70,1:10:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.11,1:10:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事情...要告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had...things to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.92,1:10:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.94,1:10:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.38,1:11:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此相爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.17,1:12:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.61,1:12:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-先生  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Monsieur! - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.16,1:12:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur!

